OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779977469
OL,3,CNo trains for three days while HS2
OL,4,Cviaduct installed
OL,6,FThe Cross City line between Birmingham
OL,7,FNew Street and Lichfield Trent Valley
OL,8,Fwill close for three days from Friday
OL,9,F29 until Sunday 31 May while a HS2
OL,10,Fviaduct is installed near the new
OL,11,FCurzon Street station.
OL,13,FNo trains will run between Lichfield
OL,14,Fand Birmingham on the north side of
OL,15,Fthe Cross City line. The line is due
OL,16,Fto reopen on Monday 1 June.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
