CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779977469
OL,3,CNo trains for three days while HS2
OL,4,Cviaduct installed
OL,6,FNetwork Rail say trains will continue
OL,7,Fto run normally between Birmingham New
OL,8,FStreet and Redditch/Bromsgrove on the
OL,9,Fsouthern section of the Cross City
OL,10,Fline, but train services between
OL,11,FBirmingham and Tame Bridge Parkway
OL,12,Fwill also be impacted.
OL,14,FRail replacement bus services will be
OL,15,Fin use and services to Rugeley Trent
OL,16,FValley will also be diverted and take
OL,17,Fslightly longer.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
