PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779977469
OL,3,CNo trains for three days while HS2
OL,4,Cviaduct installed
OL,6,FA new 150-metre-long viaduct is being
OL,7,Finstalled to carry HS2 trains towards
OL,8,FCurzon Street over the existing
OL,9,FVictorian brick viaduct that connects
OL,10,Fthe railway between Duddeston and
OL,11,FBirmingham New Street.
OL,13,FPatrick Cawley, director for On
OL,14,FNetwork Works at Network Rail and HS2,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We're asking passengers to plan
OL,16,Fahead of a three-day closure on the
OL,17,FCross City line between Birmingham and
OL,18,FLichfield, which is needed to safely
OL,19,Finstall a new HS2 viaduct deck over
OL,20,Fthe existing railway."
